Hell, I've forgotten more
about microwaving

65
00:03:02,811 --> 00:03:05,040
fat-free popcorn and watching
Sandra Bullock movies

66
00:03:05,165 --> 00:03:08,332
than you'll ever know,
but thanks for your concern, rook.

67
00:03:09,515 --> 00:03:11,607
- Let me ask you one question.
- Sure.

68
00:03:12,555 --> 00:03:15,861
Do you mind if there is
a sink full of dirty dishes?

69
00:03:16,802 --> 00:03:17,786
