it would only lead to a fight, so...

72
00:03:24,121 --> 00:03:26,539
You fight.
See, Robin and I never fight.

73
00:03:26,707 --> 00:03:28,439
- Of course you do.
- No.

74
00:03:28,564 --> 00:03:29,863
And here's the secret:

75
