we're about to get into a fight...

76
00:03:34,236 --> 00:03:36,589
Why is there
a bag of panties labeled

77
00:03:36,714 --> 00:03:39,218
"April 2008" in your closet?

78
00:03:52,336 --> 00:03:55,442
