117
00:05:56,178 --> 00:05:58,440
Hang on, Ted.
Let's hear the man out.

118
00:05:58,866 --> 00:06:00,618
Once I have her attention,

119
00:06:00,743 --> 00:06:03,028
it's time to bring out the big guns.

120
00:06:03,612 --> 00:06:05,739
Look, I love you.

121
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:09,440
But, baby, with the little
energy I have left after work,

122
00:06:09,668 --> 00:06:11,529
I want to shower you with love,

123
00:06:11,654 --> 00:06:14,123
not wash some silly dishes.

124
00:06:14,457 --> 00:06:16,657
You're right.
I'll do the dishes.

125
00:06:17,259 --> 00:06:19,044
Right after I do this.

126
00:06:25,969 --> 00:06:27,459
Now turn around.

127
00:06:31,297 --> 00:06:32,047
Firm.

128
00:06:33,977 --> 00:06:36,770
- Are you going to hit him or should I?
- He's right.

129
00:06:37,042 --> 00:06:39,555
No, he's not.
Marshall, look at me.

130
00:06:39,906 --> 00:06:42,312
