166
00:08:08,311 --> 00:08:10,957
Marshall, I'm just gonna
say this one more time.

167
00:08:11,082 --> 00:08:13,742
- It's a bad idea.
- I think it could work.

168
00:08:13,910 --> 00:08:15,573
Two more times.
It's a bad idea.

169
00:08:15,698 --> 00:08:17,826
Listen, Barney lays out
some logical points

170
00:08:17,951 --> 00:08:21,209
Lily is a reasonable woman.
I think that if I explain it to her,

171
00:08:21,334 --> 00:08:23,584
