and you'll get in a huge fight.

173
00:08:27,055 --> 00:08:28,340
- Slap bet?
- Slap bet.

174
00:08:32,062 --> 00:08:34,262
Baby, could you wash your dishes?

175
00:08:35,697 --> 00:08:37,641
Lily, I'm glad
that you bring that up.

176
00:08:41,933 --> 00:08:43,230
Can I stay here tonight?

177
00:08:45,197 --> 00:08:46,850
I'll make up the sofa, buddy.

178
00:08:56,086 --> 00:08:57,836
