but when it comes to Lily,

209
00:10:39,589 --> 00:10:41,932
I just get all... flustered.

210
00:10:43,309 --> 00:10:45,894
How could you not?
I mean, the girl's all eyes and boobs.

211
00:10:46,513 --> 00:10:49,294
What happened to the
"I'm tired after my draining day,

212
00:10:49,419 --> 00:10:52,276
