in the middle of the night,

235
00:11:46,678 --> 00:11:49,528
either turn the bathroom light on
or sit down.

236
00:11:49,653 --> 00:11:51,979
My mother does not hate you.

237
00:11:52,239 --> 00:11:54,502
She is neutral about you.

238
00:11:54,627 --> 00:11:57,158
I am not scared
of your shining impression.

239
00:11:57,283 --> 00:12:00,260
